    "The lasso's shortcomingsnamely the fact that it only collects a small sample size for high-dimensional data-are improved by the elastic net method.",
    "The elastic net method allows the incorporation of ''n'' variables up until saturation.",
    "When the variables are grouped into highly correlated groups, lasso usually selects one variable from each group while completely ignoring the others.",
    "Where the dimensional data exceed the number of samples used, the elastic net technique is best suited.",
    "(f) Principle component regression (PCR): is a principal component analysis-based regression analysis tool."
